description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Min BODYWEIGHT CALISTHENICS WORKOUT and STRETCH' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along with this 30 minute Bodyweight Calisthenics Workout to build muscle and strength. This workout finishes with dynamic mobility and static stretches to improve your overall Calisthenics training skills. This no equipment workout has both beginner Calisthenics and intermediate exercise difficulty variations to choose from.
